subtitleNullable: Dataset of 25 bird species for image classification
descriptionNullable:
This is a dataset of ~925 images of 25 common bird of India.

The challenge here is to create a model that can accurately identify these bids.

Checkout the sample notebook for inspiration. I used a pretrained VGG16 model and applied transfer learning to train the model and achieved ~92% accuracy using it

Source: https://media.ebird.org/
